@startuml stale_detection
title Stale Detection

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Analysis" as bausteinsicht_cli_analysis
participant "Loader" as bausteinsicht_model_loader
participant "Stale" as bausteinsicht_stale
participant "Git" as git

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_analysis : 1. bausteinsicht stale [--days N]
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis -> bausteinsicht_model_loader : 2. Load(model.jsonc)
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis -> bausteinsicht_stale : 3. Detect(model, threshold)
bausteinsicht_stale -> bausteinsicht_stale : 4. per element: referenced by a view? by a relationship?
bausteinsicht_stale -> git : 5. last-modified date (git log --follow)
git --> bausteinsicht_stale : 6. date, or 'no history'
bausteinsicht_stale --> bausteinsicht_cli_analysis : 7. stale elements, deterministically sorted
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis --> architect : 8. report (text / json)

@enduml
